{"tid":1392324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［瑪嘉烈醫院］眾醫護：黃金耀不代表我們","createTime":"2019-07-31T16:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T05:07:57.000Z","uid":48496,"like":92,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d0d925eab86e34069f11d3ba972a6f1c144f2288","tid":1392324,"uid":48496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:58:42.000Z","msg":"第一次出post 唔好屌咁大力<br />\n<br />\n代朋友po<br />\n對之前個瑪嘉烈醫院post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1389066\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1389066</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">前線有野講</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申，我本人唔識黃金耀<br />\n我就將我得到應該係fact check 左嘅資訊話你知<br />\n1. 佢係骨科顧問醫生，為人不嬲都係差<br />\n2. 佢係deep blue就係真嘅，但是否有義士在病房被出賣，有代查證<br />\n3. 佢出post 果日的確係有石膏course<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">4.   *最重要一點*</span></strong></span><br />\n     <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">瑪記並唔係全部人都係咁，至少我同我嘅朋友都唔係，我地會守住我地嘅崗位同專業！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人加油！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/29fSFgL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F29fSFgL.jpg&h=6c4dede3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ke0jkgM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKe0jkgM.jpg&h=4d2c2de7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rkhhRot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrkhhRot.jpg&h=65ed4c2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j65jkgP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj65jkgP.jpg&h=d61abc1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">另外提提發夢人，雖然老細要求要中立處理每個case, 而事實上我地都會堅守自己專業去做！<br />\n不過去邊間院都要小心因為乜種類既人都有</span>"},{"pid":"3c02a163c0e204fb3496c4b4c36994254f9763e5","tid":1392324,"uid":295481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:00:25.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n5/8 九巴不合作運動 正式啟動！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/abDpOOU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/abDpOOU</a><br />\n<br />\nTG group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGP%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=e670d1b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA</a>"},{"pid":"8361d2e1e05207c313a506cc635e7031df38332d","tid":1392324,"uid":48496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:02:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70f5021ee521699b71b1f30fa97c0077dd93deb9","tid":1392324,"uid":35014,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:05:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f80e0a66b28dcd8d1a8c8cad2b31f76948b31f9","tid":1392324,"uid":281466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:05:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe7baf6136528a16d62c9a206fd210385167d318","tid":1392324,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76cee64ef7cc1ba757721f7dad33938095e5ea46","tid":1392324,"uid":27008,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"70f5021ee521699b71b1f30fa97c0077dd93deb9","tid":1392324,"uid":35014,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:05:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:09:04.000Z","msg":"老實講點會無<br />\n成間醫院咁大  無可能全部人立場一樣"},{"pid":"b51a944fb4744239470d91c61a9f7b49b12e3e1d","tid":1392324,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:09:59.000Z","msg":"請你地投訴個仆街醫生"},{"pid":"d4e63396078dceb1233909dde82cb91eda91b355","tid":1392